characterDescription.skinTone: light tan skin with neutral undertones, slightly more pigmentation around the eyes and mouth, overall even complexion
characterDescription.eyeColor: deep brown eyes with slight reddish-brown hue, limbal ring darker than iris
characterDescription.eyeShape: almond-shaped eyes, slightly downturned at the outer corners, giving a serious expression, average-length eyelashes
characterDescription.hairColor: dark brown hair with subtle lighter brown highlights catching the light on the top, almost espresso color
characterDescription.hairTexture: slightly wavy hair with natural volume, medium density strands, slightly tousled
characterDescription.hairStyle: short, layered haircut, parted on the left side, with slightly longer hair on top styled forward, barely covering forehead
characterDescription.faceShape: oval face shape with soft, rounded features, slightly prominent cheekbones, defined jawline for his age
characterDescription.nose: medium-sized nose with a straight bridge, slightly rounded tip, nostrils not overly flared
characterDescription.lips: naturally pink lips, proportionate upper and lower lip size, slightly heart-shaped upper lip
characterDescription.smile: serious expression in the photo, no visible teeth, slight natural downturn at the corners of the mouth
characterDescription.eyebrows: thick dark brown eyebrows, slightly arched shape, well-groomed, follow the shape of the eye sockets
characterDescription.ears: medium-sized ears, partially visible due to hairstyle, positioned normally on the head
characterDescription.cheeks: full cheeks, slightly flushed, indicating good health
characterDescription.chin: rounded chin, proportionate to face, no cleft
characterDescription.facialProportions: balanced facial proportions, eyes take up about 1/5 of face height, nose length approximately 1/3 of face length
characterDescription.distinctiveFeatures: a small mole is located on his left cheek, below and to the left of the eye. Darker pigmentation present around the corners of the mouth.
characterDescription.overallImpression: well-groomed and serious appearance, features consistent with a child his age, with slightly mature features developing. Expresses a calmness and composure beyond his years. A naturally handsome young boy with distinct features.
characterDescription.fullDescription: This is a 6-7 year old boy with light tan skin and neutral undertones. His deep brown almond-shaped eyes are slightly downturned at the corners, and a tiny mole sits on his left cheek below his eye. His dark brown slightly wavy hair is cut short and layered, parted on the left, with subtle lighter highlights. He has an oval face shape, proportionate features, and a medium-sized nose with a straight bridge; his lips are naturally pink and full. He projects a well-groomed, serious, and calm appearance.
